sequenceDiagram
    participant I as Investor<br/>(Token Holder)
    participant P as Platform Backend
    participant O as Valuation Oracle<br/>(Chainlink)
    participant T as RWA Token
    participant R as Redemption Module
    participant AM as Asset Manager<br/>(Issuer)
    
    Note over I,AM: Trigger: Asset sold / Maturity reached
    
    P->>O: Get final valuation
    O-->>P: Sale proceeds: $15,000,000
    
    P->>T: totalSupply()
    T-->>P: 100,000 tokens outstanding
    
    P->>P: Calculate: $15M รท 100K = $150 per token
    P->>R: initiateRedemption(token, 150)
    
    AM->>R: transferUSDC(15000000)
    R->>P: Redemption funded confirmation
    
    Note over I,AM: Redemption Window Opens (60 days)
    P->>I: Notification: Redemption available<br/>@ $150 per token
    
    I->>T: approve(R, tokenBalance)
    I->>R: redeemTokens(tokenBalance)
    
    R->>T: balanceOf(Investor)
    T-->>R: 1,000 tokens
    
    R->>R: Calculate: 1,000 ร 150 = 150,000 USDC
    
    R->>T: burnFrom(Investor, 1000)
    T-->>R: Tokens burned successfully
    
    R->>I: transferUSDC(150000)
    
    R->>P: RedemptionProcessed event
    
    Note over I,AM: Post-Redemption Window (Day 61)
    P->>R: getRemainingTokens()
    R-->>P: 5,000 tokens unclaimed
    
    P->>AM: Options for unclaimed tokens:<br/>1. Extend window<br/>2. Burn remaining<br/>3. Escheat to regulator
    
    P->>P: Generate final reports:<br/>- Tax statements (Form 1099)<br/>- Investor distribution report<br/>- Audit trail documentation